  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110189120847\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110189120847\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div class=\"view\" style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'><div class=\"view\" style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><strong>\"유산균\"</strong></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">요즘엔 건강을 위해 챙겨먹는 사람들이 많습니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">이수한의원에도 유산균 챙겨드시는 분들이 많은데요,</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">변비, 소화기능, 면역력강화에도 먹지만</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">아이들 성장이나 비염 잦은 설사, 아토피질환 때문에 먹는 경우도 있습니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_249/isuhani_1397615327466PQMdF_JPEG/P4152808.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"426\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 426px; rwidth: 320px;\" id=\"20140416_249/isuhani_1397615327466PQMdF_JPEG/P4152808.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C88D4F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_249/isuhani_1397615327466PQMdF_JPEG/P4152808.JPG?type=w3\"></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><strong>※ 장은 유해균과 유익균의 전쟁터!!</strong></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">유산균은 장 뿐만 아니라 우리의 피부, 입속에도 존재하는 미생물입니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">특히 우리 장 속에는 약 100조마리의 세균이 살고있는데요,</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">장 속에 있는 유해균과 유익균이 매일매일 싸워 균형을 유지하고 있다가</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">저항력이 약할 때 병으로 나타나게되는 것이지요.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140415_44/isuhani_1397551937307vyXW6_JPEG/2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"395\" height=\"420\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border: 0px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 420px; rwidth: 395px; border-image: none;\" id=\"20140415_44/isuhani_1397551937307vyXW6_JPEG/2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C88D4F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140415_44/isuhani_1397551937307vyXW6_JPEG/2.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">염증을 치료하기 위한 항생제를 투여하는 경우,</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">내성이 생기기 쉬운 균들이 증식하게 되어 방광염이나 폐렴이 일어나기 쉬워집니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">또한 아이들은 항생제 복용시 변비가 생기는 경우도 있죠!</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"><u>따라서 항생제를 처방받는 경우엔</u></span></u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"> </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"><u>꼭 유산균을 같이 복용해주는 것이 좋습니다.</u></span></u></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><u><br /></u></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><strong>※ 나이를 먹을수록 유익균의 수는 감소합니다!!</strong></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">유익균도 40대가 지나가면서 그 수가 줄어든다는 사실 알고계신가요?!</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">매운음식과 술등의 식생활이 장을 낡아지게 만들기 때문인데요,</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">특히 노년에 약을 많이 먹게되면서 유산균이 더 많이 죽게된다고 합니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">장에 균이 없으면 정상적인 생활을 할 수 없게 되기때문에 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">나이를 먹을수록 유산균을 더 잘 챙겨드셔야겠죠!!</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">자, 그럼</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">이수한의원에는 어떤 유산균제품들이 있는지 한번 볼까요?</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"/storyphoto/Arrange.naver?type=layout&xmlPath=https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_19/isuhani_1397614533086cFhc7_XML/StoryPhoto.xml&downloadDomain=https://blogfiles.pstatic.net&width=550&height=413\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" title=\"포스트에 첨부된 스토리포토\"></iframe></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">이수한의원에는 총 네가지 제품이 진열되어 있습니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">쎌바이오틱 사의 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">듀오락</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">듀오자임</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">얌얌</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">함소아제약의 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">바이오락토&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">이수한의원에서 듀오락을 준비한 이유는</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"><u>생균으로 구성되어있고 이중코팅되어있는 제품이라</u></span></u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"> </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"><u>장까지 살아서 도달할 수 있는 제품이기때문입니다.</u></span></u></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><strong>&nbsp;- 듀오락아이비에스</strong></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_277/isuhani_1397615403421oVVFm_JPEG/P4152816.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"400\" height=\"232\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 232px; rwidth: 400px;\" id=\"20140416_277/isuhani_1397615403421oVVFm_JPEG/P4152816.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C88D4F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_277/isuhani_1397615403421oVVFm_JPEG/P4152816.JPG?type=w3\"></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">제가 먹고있는 유산균 &lt;듀오락아이비에스&gt;입니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">캡슐 형태로 되어 있고 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">유산균 함량이 </span><u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"><u>1캡슐당 110억마리 이상이기 때문에 </u></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"><u>하루 한알 복용</u></span></u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">하는 제품입니다</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_174/isuhani_13976159705596QFfr_JPEG/P4162817.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"288\" height=\"282\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 282px; rwidth: 288px;\" id=\"20140416_174/isuhani_13976159705596QFfr_JPEG/P4162817.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C88D4F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_174/isuhani_13976159705596QFfr_JPEG/P4162817.JPG?type=w3\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">한달분(30캅셀) 두달분(60캅셀) 두가지 제품으로 구성되어있습니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">캡슐을 잘 못드시는 분들은 캡슐을 뜯어서 음료에 섞어 드셔도 괜찮습니다^^</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><strong>- 듀오자임플러스</strong></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_178/isuhani_1397617234462qd2P3_JPEG/P4162820.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"249\" height=\"358\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 358px; rwidth: 249px;\" id=\"20140416_178/isuhani_1397617234462qd2P3_JPEG/P4162820.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C88D4F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_178/isuhani_1397617234462qd2P3_JPEG/P4162820.JPG?type=w3\"></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">이 제품은 듀오락아이비에스보다는 유산균이 적게 들어있습니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">대신,</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"><u>효소가 함께 들어있어서 소화가 잘 안되거나 장이 안좋은분들, </u></span></u></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"><u>특히 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14pt;\"><u><strong>변비</strong></u></span>가 있는 분들이 드시기에</u></span></u></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"><u>아주 좋은 제품입니다!!</u></span></u></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">판매하는 제품이기 때문에 이수한의원에서 가지고 있는 샘플을 뜯어보도록 할게요.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_73/isuhani_139761856980734KYS_JPEG/P4152815.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 300px; rwidth: 400px;\" id=\"20140416_73/isuhani_139761856980734KYS_JPEG/P4152815.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C88D4F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_73/isuhani_139761856980734KYS_JPEG/P4152815.JPG?type=w3\"></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">듀오자임플러스 역시 캡슐형태입니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">한통에 60캅셀로 구성되어 있구요 하루 두번 복용하는 제품으로 총 한달분량입니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">- 듀오락얌얌, 바이오락토플러스</span></strong></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_167/isuhani_1397617670245KYGms_JPEG/P4152809.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 300px; rwidth: 400px;\" id=\"20140416_167/isuhani_1397617670245KYGms_JPEG/P4152809.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C88D4F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_167/isuhani_1397617670245KYGms_JPEG/P4152809.JPG?type=w3\"></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">듀오락 얌얌.</span></strong></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">정으로 되어있는 제품으로 아이들이 씹어먹을 수 있도록 만들어진 제품입니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">합성감미료가 들어있지 않고</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">자일리톨성분이 20%정도 들어있다고 하네요^^</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 245, 152);\"><u>아침 식사 후 2알을 얌얌 먹으면 된답니다!!</u></span></u></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">맛있다고 아이가 너무 많이 먹을 수 있으니 주의해주세요~ </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"line-height: 1.8;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_251/isuhani_1397618710346JU9DJ_JPEG/detail_yamyam_140221-1-1.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"256\" height=\"266\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 266px; rwidth: 256px;\" id=\"20140416_251/isuhani_1397618710346JU9DJ_JPEG/detail_yamyam_140221-1-1.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C88D4F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_251/isuhani_1397618710346JU9DJ_JPEG/detail_yamyam_140221-1-1.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">바이오락토플러스.</span></strong></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">함소아 제품으로 분말형태로 되어있는 유산균제품입니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">튼튼한 유익균 7종이&nbsp;들어있다고 하네요^^</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">신생아,임산부부터~어른들까지 복용해도 좋은 제품입니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">주로 0세~5세 사이의 어린아이에게 처방합니다.&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">하루에 한포 식후에 복용하시면 되구요</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">가루섭취를 못하는 신생아의 경우 물이나 분유에 녹여서 복용하시면 됩니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><strong>주의!!</strong></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><strong>살아있는 생균이기때문에 뜨거운물에 타서 먹이면 안됩니다!!!</strong></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><br /></strong></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><br /></strong></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_287/isuhani_1397619050942zyxDn_JPEG/lacto_01.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"263\" height=\"234\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 234px; rwidth: 263px;\" id=\"20140416_287/isuhani_1397619050942zyxDn_JPEG/lacto_01.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C88D4F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_287/isuhani_1397619050942zyxDn_JPEG/lacto_01.jpg?type=w3\"></strong></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"line-height: 1.8;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_203/isuhani_1397619385824M4Wgy_JPEG/1.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"400\" height=\"248\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 248px; rwidth: 400px;\" id=\"20140416_203/isuhani_1397619385824M4Wgy_JPEG/1.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7C88D4F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140416_203/isuhani_1397619385824M4Wgy_JPEG/1.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;\">&nbsp;</